            <div class="insight-box">
              <h4>What this means for you:</h4>
              <p>Having ear wax is completely normal and healthy. The problems start when this protective system gets overwhelmed or disrupted.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="composition-breakdown">
            <h3>What's Actually in Ear Wax?</h3>
            <p>You don't need to memorize this, but it might help you understand why it behaves the way it does:</p>

            <div class="composition-simple">
              <div class="composition-item">
                <div class="percentage">60%</div>
