            <h3>The Bottom Line</h3>
            <p>Your wax type influences your risk of problems, but it doesn't determine your fate. Both types can cause issues when the natural cleaning process gets disrupted.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How Your Ears Should Clean Themselves -->
    <section class="natural-process-section">
