              <ul>
                <li>Wax starts getting slightly thicker</li>
                <li>Natural cleaning slows down a bit</li>
                <li>Problems take longer to resolve naturally</li>
              </ul>
              <h4>What you should do:</h4>
              <p>Start paying attention to your ear health. Consider occasional professional cleaning if you notice issues.</p>
            </div>
